<p>
  <span class="nym">Basil</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Greek</span> <i>βασιλεύς</i> 'king'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of four 4th C saints, an 8th C saint, a 9th C Byzantine emperor, a 10th C Byzantine emperor, an 11th C Byzantine emperor, a 14th C emperor of Trebizond, a 14th C grand prince of Moscow, two 15th C grand princes of Moscow, a 16th C Russian saint, and a 16th C Russian czar.</p>
</div>
  
  


